00:26:21,680 --> 00:26:23,960
不是让你白帮我 我会付钱
It's not a favour. I can pay.

348
00:26:25,900 --> 00:26:28,380
如果我想让两个女孩悄悄离开一艘货船
If I wanted to get two girls off a freighter unnoticed,

349
00:26:28,500 --> 00:26:30,020
我要怎么做?
how would I do it?

350
00:26:30,180 --> 00:26:32,380
- 多少钱? - 什么多少钱? 
- How much? - How much what?

351
00:26:32,540 --> 00:26:35,320
你说你会付钱 多少钱?  
You said you'd pay. How much?

352
00:26:35,321 --> 00:26:37,460
十块钱 这价格很合理
Ten. It's a fair price.

353
00:26:39,940 --> 00:26:41,900
这叫做循环取货
It's called a milk run.

354
00:26:42,060 --> 00:26:44,380
皮条客们会把妓女们带到货船上
Pimps will take the working girls out to the freighter

355
00:26:44,500 --> 00:26:46,340
给那些不能上岸的船员们
for crew who can't make it ashore.

356
00:26:46,460 --> 00:26:49,020
然后他们会把她们带回来的 是吗?
Then they bring them back, yeah?

357
00:26:49,180 --> 00:26:51,556
好吧 - 就这样? 
OK.  - That's it? 

358
00:26:51,557 --> 00:26:53,140
这钱赚得真容易啊
Oh, that's easy money.

359
00:26:53,300 --> 00:26:55,418
我要你查出昨晚在猎户星号货船上
I need you to find out 

360
00:26:55,419 --> 00:26:56,540
有没有循环取货
if there was a milk run to Orion Star last night.

361
00:26:56,660 --> 00:26:58,940
我还有生意要做
I got a business to run.

362
00:26:59,100 --> 00:27:01,100
我觉得两个女孩子在船上被绑架了
I think two girls were kidnapped off the ship.

363
00:27:01,220 --> 00:27:03,620
绑架的人是为了勒索赎金
They're being held for ransom.

364
00:27:07,540 --> 00:27:09,020
你先帮我搬这些货
Help me with this first.

365
00:28:18,780 --> 00:28:20,660
是谁指使你的?
Who are you working for?

366
00:28:20,780 --> 00:28:22,500
什么?
What?

367
00:28:22,620 --> 00:28:26,180
我丈夫被人谋杀了
Someone murdered my husband,

368
00:28:26,340 --> 00:28:31,220
而你告诉我这个故事 这个捏造的故事
and now you arrive with this story, this fabrication.

369
00:28:31,380 --> 00:28:33,362
是为了玷污他的名声 
Is this to muddy his reputation, 

370
00:28:33,363 --> 00:28:35,940
好让我不去追究凶手是谁吗?
so I don't go look for his killer?

371
00:28:36,100 --> 00:28:40,580
- 不是 - 你怎么拿到他的表的?
- No. - How did you get his watch?

372
00:28:40,700 --> 00:28:42,140
你到底有什么目的?
What do you really want?

373
00:28:44,700 --> 00:28:48,140
他根本没有情妇 是吗?
There was no affair, was there?

374
00:28:48,260 --> 00:28:51,540
也没人怀孕 没有小孩 对不对?
No pregnancy? No child?

375
00:28:51,660 --> 00:28:53,620
妈咪?
Mummy?

376
00:28:57,020 --> 00:28:59,420
你先回去睡觉吧


377
00:28:59,620 --> 00:29:01,920
妈妈等下讲故事给你听


378
00:29:19,820 --> 00:29:23,900
他死的那晚 来过这里
On the night he died, he was here.

379
00:29:25,700 --> 00:29:28,980
他通常在周三过来
He usually came on Wednesdays.

380
00:29:29,100 --> 00:29:33,540
每周三 他都说去打麻将
Wednesdays, he played mahjong.

381
00:29:35,980 --> 00:29:38,700
但是那晚我没想到他会来
But I wasn't expecting him that night.

382
00:29:38,820 --> 00:29:43,140
他看上去很忧虑 甚至有点恐惧
He seemed worried, even scared.

383
00:29:43,300 --> 00:29:46,660
他确信有人在跟踪他
He believed that someone was following him,

384
00:29:46,780 --> 00:29:49,860
想要伤害他
that they meant to do him harm.

385
00:29:51,980 --> 00:29:54,100
他走之前 给了我这块表
Before he left, he gave me the watch.

386
00:29:57,340 --> 00:30:02,280
他说如果出了什么事 就把表给你
He said to give it to you, should anything happen.

387
00:30:03,300 --> 00:30:08,240
我本想留着那块表 为了我们的儿子
I wanted to keep it, for our boy.

388
00:30:10,040 --> 00:30:12,180
但我做不到
But I couldn't.

389
00:30:12,340 --> 00:30:14,820
我没钱了
I've run out of money.

390
00:30:16,940 --> 00:30:18,060
我无路可走
I've nowhere else to turn.

391
00:30:19,180 --> 00:30:20,700
请你等等
Please.

392
00:30:25,260 --> 00:30:26,665
他爱你吗?
Did he love you? 

393
00:30:29,066 --> 00:30:31,220
他爱我们的儿子
He loved our boy.

394
00:30:31,340 --> 00:30:33,340
他爱你吗?
Did he love you?

395
00:30:34,341 --> 00:30:38,380
他不爱我 但他爱我们的儿子
No, he didn't. But he loved our son.

396
00:30:39,140 --> 00:30:42,060
他说孩子是你一直渴望得到的
He said it was the one thing that you've always wished for.

397
00:30:46,860 --> 00:30:48,361
你们在一起多久? 
How long?

398
00:30:50,132 --> 00:30:53,400
不久 就几个晚上 仅此而已
Not long. A few nights, no more.

399
00:30:54,840 --> 00:30:56,576
求你了  
Please. 

400
00:30:57,277 --> 00:31:02,020
你尽管恨我吧 但别恨孩子
Hate me all you want, but not the boy.

401
00:31:03,140 --> 00:31:05,180
那温斯顿呢?
What about Winston?

402
00:31:07,300 --> 00:31:11,100
我要怎样体谅我的丈夫呢?
What do I feel for my husband?

403
00:31:27,100 --> 00:31:29,740
艾奎斯特正在替我凑赎金
Edquist is wiring the ransom money to me now.

404
00:31:29,741 --> 00:31:30,700
我一小时内就能拿到钱了
I'll have it in an hour.

405
00:31:30,860 --> 00:31:32,780
你本可以不用惹这些麻烦的
You could have saved yourself some trouble.

406
00:31:33,940 --> 00:31:36,220
我差点没渴死
Oh! A man could die of thirst around here.

407
00:31:36,340 --> 00:31:37,060
多谢 安格
Thanks, Ange.

408
00:31:37,220 --> 00:31:41,740
那个叫艾奎斯特的女孩怎么样了?
So, what's the latest on the Edquist girl?

409
00:31:42,300 --> 00:31:44,900
- 官方消息 无可奉告 - 非官方的呢?
- Officially, no comment. - Unofficially?

410
00:31:45,620 --> 00:31:46,820
去你的
Bugger off.

411
00:31:48,220 --> 00:31:49,587
所以你有什么消息给我 
So you got something for me, 

412
00:31:49,588 --> 00:31:51,080
还是我用我现有的?
or do I run with what I got?

413
00:31:51,085 --> 00:31:52,963
"牧场主女儿的黑社会恐怖故事" 
'Grazier's Daughter Triad Horror'. 

414
00:31:52,964 --> 00:31:54,020
这名字就说明了一切
This story writes itself.

415
00:31:54,140 --> 00:31:55,780
我很快就回来
Back in a sec.

416
00:31:59,820 --> 00:32:02,260
- 打听到什么了吗? - 一个人名
- What have you got? - A name.

417
00:32:02,420 --> 00:32:04,260
他带了两个女孩出去 却带着四个女孩回来
He went out with two girls, came back with four,

418
00:32:04,380 --> 00:32:05,740
还有几个船员
along with a few crew.

419
00:32:05,900 --> 00:32:07,140
- 这是他带她们去的地方 - 谢谢
- This is where he dropped them. - Thanks.

420
00:32:07,260 --> 00:32:10,900
嘿 要把她们带回来哦
Hey, bring them back, yeah?

421
00:33:23,200 --> 00:33:24,200
你好吗?


422
00:33:26,400 --> 00:33:29,200
你有见过这些女孩吗?


423
00:33:32,180 --> 00:33:33,660
霍克!
Hawk!

424
00:34:31,400 --> 00:34:32,880
有人吗?
Hello?

425
00:34:36,800 --> 00:34:39,280
好了好了 没事了 我不会伤害你的
It's OK, it's OK, it's alright. I'm not gonna hurt you.

426
00:34:39,440 --> 00:34:41,520
放轻松 冷静
Just relax, relax.

427
00:34:48,480 --> 00:34:50,899
卡米拉? 我叫山姆 
Camilla? I'm Sam. 

428
00:34:50,900 --> 00:34:53,560
我是来救你们离开这儿的
I'm going to get you out of here.

429
00:34:55,040 --> 00:34:57,840
找到吉娜了吗? 她还好吗?
Have you found Gina? Is she alright?

430
00:35:07,240 --> 00:35:10,280
我上上下下找遍了那里 就是不见吉娜的踪迹
I searched the place top to bottom. There was no sign of Gina.

431
00:35:10,440 --> 00:35:14,696
那么卡米拉最后一次见她是什么时候?  
So when did Camilla see her last?  

432
00:35:14,697 --> 00:35:16,040
大概两小时前
About two hours ago.

433
00:35:16,160 --> 00:35:17,760
她说她们被分开关押
She said they were kept separate

434
00:35:17,920 --> 00:35:20,080
这样就不能一起逃跑了
so they wouldn't escape without each other.

435
00:35:23,840 --> 00:35:24,960
她在这儿吗?   
Is she here?  

436
00:35:24,961 --> 00:35:26,080
她在跟她父亲通电话
She's on the phone with her father.

437
00:35:27,440 --> 00:35:29,680
我是澳大利亚领事馆的斯图尔特・安德森
Stuart Anderson from the Australian Consulate.

438
00:35:29,800 --> 00:35:31,160
很高兴看到你安全归来
We're so glad that you're safe.

439
00:35:31,320 --> 00:35:33,320
爸爸 有个政府部门的人来了
Daddy, there's a man from the government here.

440
00:35:33,440 --> 00:35:35,600
他想跟你通话
He wants to talk to you.

441
00:35:39,760 --> 00:35:41,720
你还好吗? 你父亲呢?
You alright? How's your father?

442
00:35:41,840 --> 00:35:43,280
他很生气
Angry.

443
00:35:43,400 --> 00:35:45,480
不过很欣慰我没事
Glad that I'm OK.

444
00:35:45,640 --> 00:35:48,160
你说船长跟这件事无关?
So you were saying the Captain wasn't involved?

445
00:35:48,280 --> 00:35:50,960
不 呃...
No, um...

446
00:35:51,080 --> 00:35:53,680
他曾试图...
After he tried...

447
00:35:53,840 --> 00:35:56,240
我只是再也不能呆在那艘船上了
Just couldn't be on that ship anymore.

448
00:35:56,360 --> 00:35:58,040
没事 我们理解
It's OK. We understand.

449
00:35:58,200 --> 00:36:01,720
霍克说他会在船长眼皮子底下偷偷带我们下船
Hawk said he could get us off the ship without the Captain knowing.

450
00:36:01,840 --> 00:36:04,000
他的一番话让我们觉得新加坡很给力
He made Singapore sound so exciting.

451
00:36:04,160 --> 00:36:07,600
植物园里的抽彩和猴子
The Raffles and monkeys in the Botanical Gardens.

452
00:36:07,720 --> 00:36:10,800
那些都是吉娜想要看的
That's what Gina wanted to see.

453
00:36:10,920 --> 00:36:13,440
她会没事的 是吧?
She's going to be OK, isn't she?

454
00:36:13,600 --> 00:36:16,512
山姆 我可以跟你私下说两句吗? 
Sam, can I have a word? 

455
00:36:16,513 --> 00:36:17,240
怎么了?
Why, what's the matter?

456
00:36:17,400 --> 00:36:22,360
情况很微妙 是关于艾奎斯特先生的钱
It's a delicate situation. Mr Edquist's money.

457
00:36:23,880 --> 00:36:26,980
他对于这笔钱怎么花要求很明确
He's being very specific about what it can and cannot be used for.

458
00:36:27,000 --> 00:36:28,386
他在说什么?  
What is he talking about?  

459
00:36:28,387 --> 00:36:30,279
他不会帮吉娜付赎金的
He won't pay for Gina's release.

460
00:36:30,280 --> 00:36:32,200
- 什么?! - 听着 我很遗憾
- What?! - Look, I am sorry.

461
00:36:32,360 --> 00:36:34,280
他怪吉娜让你卷入这个麻烦
He blames Gina for getting you into this mess.

462
00:36:34,400 --> 00:36:36,000
我会跟堪培拉的人谈
I will speak to Canberra.

463
00:36:36,160 --> 00:36:38,360
我会试着用别的方法来筹齐这笔赎金
I will try and raise the ransom money some other way.

464
00:36:38,520 --> 00:36:40,160
- 这要多长时间? - 很长
- How long will that take? - Too long.

465
00:36:43,800 --> 00:36:47,760
不 山姆 这笔钱已经不能用了
No, Sam. This money is quarantined.

466
00:36:49,080 --> 00:36:51,360
不要再想了
It is off the table.

467
00:37:32,360 --> 00:37:35,720
安德森先生 真的有必要这样吗?
Mr Anderson, is this really necessary?

468
00:37:35,880 --> 00:37:37,920
如果出了什么岔子 我有不在场证明
If things go bad, then I have an alibi.

469
00:37:38,040 --> 00:37:40,000
你们从我这里偷了那笔钱
You stole that money from me.

470
00:37:44,520 --> 00:37:47,102
安德森先生不和我们一起吗?  
Mr Anderson not joining us? 

471
00:37:47,103 --> 00:37:48,480
不了 他现在很忙
No, he's tied up right now.

472
00:41:37,420 --> 00:41:39,820
- 你怎么看? - 我们先看看什么情况
- What do you think? - Let's see what's going on first.

473
00:41:39,940 --> 00:41:41,300
如果我们冲进去 他可能会紧张
If we bust in, he might panic.

474
00:41:56,380 --> 00:41:58,540
他在屋里 里面还有其他人
He's in there with at least one other.

475
00:42:39,080 --> 00:42:44,000
那是凯・索的人 我会组织突袭
That was Kay Song's men. I'll organise a raid.

476
00:42:44,320 --> 00:42:45,720
她可能活不了那么长
She's not going to live that long.

477
00:42:47,160 --> 00:42:49,240
- 你去哪儿? - 去试试把她带回来
- Where are you going? - To try and get her back.

478
00:42:49,360 --> 00:42:50,840
嘿 山姆!
Hey, Sam!

479
00:43:14,440 --> 00:43:16,440
- 嘿 - 敢碰我 你就死定了
- Hey. - Touch me, you're dead.

480
00:43:29,760 --> 00:43:33,520
来坐吧 国际友人 我们有很多要庆祝的呢
Oh, come sit, my Ang mo friend. We have much to celebrate.

481
00:43:35,880 --> 00:43:38,840
今天我赚了不少钱
Today I made a lot of money,

482
00:43:39,000 --> 00:43:42,880
干掉了仇敌 恢复了我爷爷的名声
spilled the blood of my enemy, restored my grandfather's honour.

483
00:43:43,000 --> 00:43:45,480
我都不知道要怎样感谢你
I'm not quite sure how to thank you.

484
00:43:45,600 --> 00:43:47,160
告诉我那个女孩在哪
Just tell me where the girl is.

485
00:43:47,320 --> 00:43:50,400
我们从不绑架白人女孩 没人跟你说过吗?
We don't kidnap white girls. Didn't anyone tell you?

486
00:43:50,560 --> 00:43:52,720
那她到底在哪?
Then where is she?

487
00:43:52,880 --> 00:43:57,760
这就是你的计划? 来这里向我提要求?
So that's your plan? Come in here, demand things from me.

488
00:43:58,920 --> 00:44:01,960
你应该感激我没当场把你干掉
You should be grateful I don't kill you where you stand.

489
00:44:03,280 --> 00:44:04,880
你刚刚还说你要谢谢我
You just said you wanted to thank me.

490
00:44:08,200 --> 00:44:10,120
你没看到吗?
You don't see, do you?

491
00:44:11,240 --> 00:44:16,200
我的人到的时候 你的公主正和霍克数钱呢
When my men arrived, your princess was counting money with Hawk.

492
00:44:17,760 --> 00:44:19,800
坐下吃点吧
So sit and eat.

493
00:44:20,840 --> 00:44:23,560
别为她流泪了
Oh, don't go shedding tears for her.

494
00:44:32,720 --> 00:44:34,920
卡米拉没事 就是担心吉娜
Camilla's fine, just worried about Gina.

495
00:44:35,080 --> 00:44:37,960
安德森先生情况越来越差了
Mr Anderson's gone into a steep decline.

496
00:44:38,080 --> 00:44:40,040
哈 我保证他会活着
Ha. I'm sure he'll live.

497
00:44:40,200 --> 00:44:43,160
我不明白 她会去哪?
I don't understand. Where would she go?

498
00:44:44,240 --> 00:44:47,480
吉娜说了什么? 霍克告诉他们的地方?
What did Gina say? The places Hawk told them about?

499
00:44:47,640 --> 00:44:51,600
- 是的 抽彩和... - 植物园的猴子
- Yes, Raffles and...- The monkeys in the garden.

500
00:45:00,560 --> 00:45:01,980
吉娜・克肖?
Gina Kershaw?

501
00:45:02,000 --> 00:45:05,820
拜托 别跑了 没事的
Please, don't run. It's alright.

502
00:45:05,840 --> 00:45:07,680
你是谁?
Who are you?

503
00:45:07,800 --> 00:45:11,480
我是山姆 我刚刚和卡米拉在一起来着
I'm Sam. I was just with Camilla.

504
00:45:14,360 --> 00:45:18,280
- 她怎么样? - 她没事
- How is she? - She's fine.

505
00:45:19,440 --> 00:45:21,680
她很担心你
She's worried about you.

506
00:45:23,000 --> 00:45:24,760
我知道
I know.

507
00:45:32,560 --> 00:45:35,720
你跟霍克一起参与了这件事 对吗?
So you and Hawk were in this together, were you?

508
00:45:38,080 --> 00:45:40,840
她是你最好的朋友 为什么你要那么做?
She's your best friend. Why would you do that?

509
00:45:44,080 --> 00:45:48,040
她和我 我们计划了一年了
She and I, we planned it for a year.

510
00:45:49,200 --> 00:45:53,600
我省吃俭用
I saved up every penny I had.

511
00:45:53,760 --> 00:45:58,100
我们俩 一路去了伦敦
The two of us, all the way to London.

512
00:45:58,120 --> 00:46:02,200
我们要告诉全世界我们能独立完成
We were going to show the world we could do it on our own.

513
00:46:07,120 --> 00:46:12,120
船长袭击她以后 她一心想回家
When the Captain attacked her,she just wanted to go home.

514
00:46:14,680 --> 00:46:17,120
我恳求她
I begged her.

515
00:46:18,240 --> 00:46:20,249
对她来说钱不是问题 
Money was never a problem for her 

516
00:46:20,250 --> 00:46:22,660
但我没足够的钱一个人生存
and I couldn't afford to stay on alone,

517
00:46:22,680 --> 00:46:25,360
如果我回去了 我就一无所有
and if I went home, I would be left with nothing

518
00:46:25,520 --> 00:46:28,480
然后我又得重新开始省吃俭用
and I would have to start saving all over again.

519
00:46:32,720 --> 00:46:35,600
我们之间有约定
We made a promise to each other.

520
00:46:52,300 --> 00:46:55,700
哈里森 来杯威士忌?
Harrison. Whisky?

