00:47:16,431 --> 00:47:18,940
关于在兰利总部的人的动向
on what our friends at Langley are doing.

526
00:47:19,100 --> 00:47:22,380
每周五交给我 一份也不能少 明白了么?
Every Friday. Don't miss a report. Are we clear?

