那你去吧
Well, off you go, then.

540
00:48:43,500 --> 00:48:45,014
好了 我把吉娜交给了斯图尔特 
Well, I left Gina with Stuart. 

541
00:48:45,015 --> 00:48:47,020
没提绑架的事
Didn't mention the kidnapping.

542
00:48:47,180 --> 00:48:50,100
我想如果他够聪明 他自己会发现的
I suppose if he's smart enough,he'll work it out for himself.

543
00:48:56,340 --> 00:48:59,280
你没事吧?
You alright?

544
00:48:59,300 --> 00:49:01,380
你知道吗?
Did you know?

545
00:49:02,460 --> 00:49:04,660
温斯顿的外遇?
Winston's affair?

546
