我都不能朝他发火
I don't even get to scream at him

549
00:49:21,660 --> 00:49:24,940
给他一巴掌 把他踢出家门
and slap his face and chase him out of the house.

550
00:49:33,980 --> 00:49:38,960
他全家人只想让他离开我 重新开始生活
His whole family just wanted him to leave me and take a new wife.

551
00:49:39,780 --> 00:49:43,100
这就是我们的文化传统
That's the way it is in our culture.

552
00:49:43,220 --> 00:49:46,260
谁会要一个不能生育的女人?
Who wants a barren woman?

553
00:49:52,140 --> 00:49:54,780
一切都毁了
Everything's been ruined.

554
00:50:14,340 --> 00:50:16,180
好糟糕的一天
What an awful day.

555
00:50:22,900 --> 00:50:24,580
克莱尔
Claire.

556
00:50:29,340 --> 00:50:30,820
怎么了?
What?

557
00:50:32,820 --> 00:50:34,700
我希望我们能住在一起
I wish we could live together.

558
00:50:35,700 --> 00:50:38,020
塔克沃思女士觉得这不是个好主意
Lady Tuckworth doesn't think it's a good idea.

559
00:50:40,340 --> 00:50:41,820
她说的没错
She's right.

560
00:50:44,700 --> 00:50:47,900
行不通的
It's not going to work.

561
00:50:49,460 --> 00:50:51,020
别离开弗兰克
Don't leave Frank.

562
00:50:51,140 --> 00:50:52,900
这...
It's...

563
00:50:55,980 --> 00:50:57,460
这里的生活不是你想象的那样
It's not a life here.

564
00:50:57,580 --> 00:51:00,700
你... 你不属于这里
You don't... you don't belong here.

565
00:51:05,060 --> 00:51:06,820
你还没告诉他吧?
You haven't told him yet, have you?

566
00:51:06,980 --> 00:51:10,940
- 所以你仍然可以... - 没错
- So you can still... - Yes, of course.

567
00:51:15,780 --> 00:51:17,420
你能理解吗?
Does that make sense?

568
00:51:19,300 --> 00:51:21,900
对 理解
Yeah, it makes sense.

569
00:51:41,180 --> 00:51:43,540
她被人捅了 是他干的 山姆
She's been stabbed.He did it, Sam.

570
00:51:43,660 --> 00:51:45,380
他身上有血 是她的血
He had blood on him.Hers.

571
00:51:45,540 --> 00:51:46,860
谋杀后逃离现场 你还有什么话要说
Any comment on getting away with murder

572
00:51:47,020 --> 00:51:48,340
因为澳洲政府...
'cause the Australian government's...

